channel.title: Uploading Files :: CID guide website
channel.description: To bring your file into the Laser Cutters first go to https://glowforge.com. There you will see a website with many options. If the computer is not signed into glowforge, have an adult sign you in. If the computer is signed in, hit the Create button, which will take you to a new menu. there you will see a list of projects, which you can select to open, or in the top left, there is a Create a New Design button for your own designs.
